    <div class="about-section">
        <div class="about-header">Welcome to the Flight Dashboard!</div>
        <div class="about-text">
            This tool is designed to help you explore and analyze flight data with ease. Here's a quick overview of what you can do:
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <span class="highlight">Check Flights:</span> In this section, you can select the departing and arriving cities from the dropdown menus and click the <b>"Search"</b> button to see a table of flights between the selected cities, including the flight name, departing time, arriving time, duration, and price.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="highlight">Flights Analytics:</span> Gain insights into various aspects of flights between selected cities with the following analyses:
                    <ul>
                        <li><b>Price Distribution:</b> View a bar chart showing the average price of flights from different airlines between the selected cities.</li>
                        <li><b>Flight Frequency per Airline:</b> See a pie chart illustrating the number of flights each airline operates between the chosen cities.</li>
                        <li><b>Average Flight Duration per Airline:</b> Check out a bar chart displaying the average flight duration for each airline.</li>
                        <li><b>Peak Departure Times:</b> Analyze the busiest times for flight departures with a bar chart showing the frequency of flights at different times of the day.</li>
                        <li><b>Price Trend by Time of the Day:</b> Discover how flight prices vary throughout the day with a line chart showing average prices at different departure times.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="highlight">How to Use:</div>
            <ol>
                <li>Navigate to the <b>"Flights Analytics"</b> section.</li>
                <li>Select the source and destination cities from the dropdown menus.</li>
                <li>Explore the visualizations to gain insights into flight patterns, prices, and durations.</li>
            </ol>
            We hope you find this dashboard helpful for your travel planning and flight analysis needs!
        </div>
        <div class="signature">Created by Aditya </div>
